data.description: Located in the lovely hamlet of Nanuet in the desirable town of Clarkstown. Nanuet school district. The amazing and beautiful peaceful setting sits this three-bedroom and two-bath ranch home all one-level living. Updated marble kitchen with stainless steel appliances and oak cabinets.  Travertine marble island with stone backsplash. Living room with Bay window creating a comfortable alcove. Attractive gas fireplace that can be used year-round. Updated Andersen windows throughout. A beautiful backyard with a koi pond is a tranquil oasis that combines beauty with serene water elements. Lush and well-manicured space featuring the centerpiece of this waterfall and pond.  Comfortable seating area which we can call our outdoor living room with gazebo, fan, lights and flat screen TV ready for the family to enjoy  Fabulous outdoor entertainment all year long.  Home is equipped with a whole house  Briggs and Stratton 5500 Watt Generator.
